  "texts": [
    "The prompts allowed students to create responses, think more critically, and connect ideas together, which in turn allowed them to understand and remember educational concepts better.",
    "According to Jo (2024) and Ruiz-Rojas et al. (2024), this helped participants stay on task and maintain a clear direction during interactions with the tutor bot, thus creating a reliable learning environment.",
    "Besides, consistent prompts guarantee the timeliness and relevance of the students' feedback for reinforcement purposes, which are instrumental in timely revisions of misconceptions (Chang et al., 2023).",
    "In response to Research Question 2 (RQ2), although ChatGPT technology already presents promising results related to personalized learning support, significant limitations in its capabilities can still be found (Lo, 2023; Zhang & Tur, 2024).",
    "Chat-GPT is able to provide personalized feedback for learners' questions, keep previous interactions to maintain the continuity of the conversation and provide scaffolding tailored to the strengths and weaknesses of each learner (Dai et al., 2023; Pesovski et al., 2024)."
  ],
